item.title: Data: Walk through VMware Tanzu RabbitMQ for Kubernetes
item.description: VMware’s Yaron Parasol and Chunyi Lyu walk through VMware Tanzu RabbitMQ for Kubernetes. A custom Kubernetes cluster operator makes it easy to run Tanzu RabbitMQ on any certified Kubernetes distribution, including all of the VMware Tanzu Editions.
